#

Mixed Berry and Yogurt Crepes

25 min
$12.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Protein

Cuisine:

French

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastDessertEasyFruity

Description

Delicate crepes filled with a luscious mix of fresh berries and creamy yogurt, perfect for a sweet breakfast or dessert!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • fresh mixed berries (strawberries, blueberries, raspberries): 1 cup
  • plain yogurt: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
